data.description: Welcome home to this Schuylkill Valley charmer! Upon entering this home, you will be greeted by the spacious living room - ideal for entertaining! The kitchen is bright and open, and leads out to the large backyard. The first floor also features a full bathroom and two bedrooms. Upstairs you will find two generously sized bedrooms. The basement area is finished with a full bathroom and plenty of extra space for a second living area. The front porch is welcoming and perfect for decorating each season. near to major routes.
